  <rte>
    <name>Skiddaw and Glenderaterra Beck from Underscar</name>
	<desc>Skiddaw is the fourth highest peak in Lakeland. This Lake District walk combines a remarkably easy and straightforward route of ascent with an interesting return.</desc>
